msgctxt "an5.158:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 5 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 5 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.158:0.2"
msgid "16. Saddhammavagga "
msgstr "16. The True Teaching "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an5.158:0.3"
msgid "158. Sārajjasutta "
msgstr "158. Timidity "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
#. VAR: okkanto → okkamanto (mr)
msgctxt "an5.158:1.1"
msgid "“Pañcahi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato bhikkhu sārajjaṃ okkanto hoti. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, a mendicant with five qualities is overcome by timidity. "

msgctxt "an5.158:1.2"
msgid "Katamehi pañcahi? "
msgstr "What five? "

msgctxt "an5.158:1.3"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu assaddho hoti, dussīlo hoti, appassuto hoti, kusīto hoti, duppañño hoti. "
msgstr "It’s when a mendicant is faithless, unethical, with little learning, lazy, and witless. "

msgctxt "an5.158:1.4"
msgid "Imehi kho, bhikkhave, pañcahi, dhammehi samannāgato bhikkhu sārajjaṃ okkanto hoti. "
msgstr "A mendicant with these five qualities is overcome by timidity. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli3.184, sc2
msgctxt "an5.158:2.1"
msgid "Pañcahi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato bhikkhu visārado hoti. "
msgstr "A mendicant with five qualities is self-assured. "

msgctxt "an5.158:2.2"
msgid "Katamehi pañcahi? "
msgstr "What five? "

msgctxt "an5.158:2.3"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu saddho hoti, sīlavā hoti, bahussuto hoti, āraddhavīriyo hoti, paññavā hoti. "
msgstr "It’s when a mendicant is faithful, ethical, learned, energetic, and wise. "

msgctxt "an5.158:2.4"
msgid "Imehi kho, bhikkhave, pañcahi dhammehi samannāgato bhikkhu visārado hotī”ti. "
msgstr "A mendicant with these five qualities is self-assured.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.158:2.5"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

